item.title: Summoner Showcase -- Issue #30 -- Every Day A New Adventure
item.description:
Summoner Showcase -- Issue #30 -- Every Day A New Adventure
Play League of Legends FREE at http://signup.leagueoflegends.com/?ref=ss30 But don't stop there! Check out the full submissions and participate! Metal League of Legends [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L7L7M_PPzJs] Tyrraell puts a new spin on an old favorite, providing not piano but hard-rockin' riffs to coin the League of Legends experience. To those about to rock, we salute you! Nocturne [http://anarki3000.deviantart.com/#/d3gjheh] Anarki3000, you have kept us waiting. We nearly forgot how incredible your fan art is, and then you come through to surprise and awe us once more. Hats off to you! Caitlyn Cosplay [http://ragamuffyn.deviantart.com/#/d3fh8j8] Ragamuffyn is armed and ready to take out the competition, and maybe a minion or two. Spain's incredible cosplayers grow more amazing by the day! You Awaken in Summoner's Rift [http://www.leagueoflegends.com/board/showthread.php?t=747711] HylianDanny, bless his roleplaying soul, is hosting an interactive text adventure where any summoner can decide their fate on the Fields of Justice ... by face checking the brush, or creating something called a Potion Flux. Jump in and enjoy. Zombie Mundo [http://www.leagueoflegends.com/board/attachment.php?attachmentid=169330&d=1304801691] Why, oh why did nobody think of this before Doomsupporter? Zombies are a smash hit, and using the words "smash hit" when discussing Mundo would be an understatement. We look forward to new submissions of all kinds in our Summoner_Showcase@Riotgames.com inbox, so don't let us down! Until next time, embrace your inner adventure gamer - embrace a turret while you're at it - and we'll see you next week!
